# API Test Cases

## API-TC-001 — GET pokemon/ditto
Pre-Conditions: Postman installed; Internet connection
Request: GET https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon/ditto
Expected Result: 
- Status code = 200
- name = "ditto"
Actual Result: PASS
Notes: Verified via Postman

## API-TC-002 — GET pokemon?limit=10
Pre-Conditions: Postman installed; Internet connection
Request: GET https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon?limit=10
Expected Result:
- Status code = 200
- results count = 10
Actual Result: PASS
Notes: Verified via Postman

## API-TC-003 — POST /posts
Pre-Conditions: Postman installed; Internet connection
Request: POST https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts
Body:
{
  "title": "QA test",
  "body": "This is a test post",
  "userId": 1
}
Expected Result:
- Status = 201
- Response contains id
Actual Result: PASS
Notes: Verified via Postman

## API-TC-004 — GET invalid pokemon
Pre-Conditions: Postman installed; Internet connection
Request: GET https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon/invalid-pokemon-name
Expected Result:
- Status = 404
Actual Result: PASS
Notes: Verified via Postman
